{"title":"林中之战——题白乙化司令","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"林中之战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——题白乙化司令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九三九年夏天：我曾在白乙化司令部中住过一个时期，此时正值雨季，我们常因雨天作夜谈。从此，我知道他是东北人，一个大学生，当时他是团长，后来愈战愈有名，为平北根据地创造者之一。惟不幸于四关之战中牺牲。死时年仅二十八岁。民间关于他的传说很多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白司令爱戴草帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也爱自挎大枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常独人只马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走访民间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天，红日正出山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道的金光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照射那果木林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他坐在林内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和老杜闲谈（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老杜说：“年青人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子垂到胸前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，胡子好美！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白说：“这不算美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我叫你看美的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我的枪法！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老杜刚抬起眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一声枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿落两颗苹果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正当戏笑之时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的骑兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿河而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行势如雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二人未及多想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马蹄响到眼前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈是危难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈是勇敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是老白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十多岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多才多艺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这也是老白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白他这时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诈进取退"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马虽飞来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他偏要迎个面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他走出树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎马便一枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起一颗头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚下河去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是他回身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再闪进林内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在树林之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人追"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他回枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又立起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久他突了围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄走到河边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他跳下河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑着，笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮过了水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他过河时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水如金镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照进一个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这人极高大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子又极长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈笑风生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中长着天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）老杜是过去平西的杜伯华，对中医也很有研究，后调至军区任卫生部副部长，亦不幸病故。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}